  <summary>4/25/2002--Introduced.
Amends Federal provisions concerning State participation in the National Guard Challenge Program (a civilian youth opportunities program conducted by the Secretary of Defense) to: (1) provide a permanent matching funds level of 75 percent of the costs of operating the State program during a fiscal year; and (2) authorize annual appropriations for the Program.</summary>
